.Xr pthread_create 3 ,
.Xr pthreads 3
.Sh STANDARDS
.Fn pthread_attr_setstackaddr
and
.Fn pthread_attr_getstackaddr
conform to ISO/IEC 9945-1 ANSI/IEEE
